name: RiskCube
long_description:
RiskCube Insurance is building a modern, AI-native insurance brokerage — designed to help businesses access smarter, faster, and more transparent coverage. We were founded to protect the financial well-being of hardworking American businesses. 
We're currently in the licensing process in California and will be launching soon. Our initial focus will be on business property and compliance insurance.

If you're a carrier interested in partnering with us, we'd love to connect — please send us a DM!
